# GisForge Core

Angular 19 standalone + Spartan UI + Tailwind v4 + Supabase + signals.

## Golden rule

1 feature = 1 folder in `features/` = 1 lazy route = 1 data service.

## Structure

- `core/` — auth, layout, supabase (singletons, no business UI)
- `shared/ui/` — Spartan Helm components only
- `features/<name>/` — page, service, routes, types

## Naming

`<feature>.page.ts`, `<feature>.service.ts`, `<feature>.routes.ts`, `<feature>.types.ts`

## Forbidden

- NgModules
- Supabase calls in components (use services)
- Static imports of all pages in app.routes
- Manual edits to `database.types.ts`
- `confirm()` for delete — use hlm-dialog

## Reference

Full rules in `AGENTS.md`. CRUD pattern: `features/users`.
